{"tid":2395852,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"應唔應該寫信俾分左手超過十年嘅Ex","createTime":"2021-02-05T07:09:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T14:02:46.000Z","uid":254852,"like":2,"dislike":170,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"f21950c64d7c2cba72cb1e67640f60af770d63b0","tid":2395852,"uid":254852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T07:09:09.000Z","msg":"情況係咁：<br />\n當年我出國讀書，期間佢識左第二個，瞞住我一排然後突然分手，後來我地無Fd做。<br />\n<br />\n過左幾年之後，我無晒嬲嘅感覺，生活如常，後來結左婚，有埋小朋友。<br />\n<br />\n後來，又經朋友得知，佢去左荷蘭讀書，畢業無乜野撈，但係又因為簽証要求等，迫住開公司接job做，加上疫情，擔心佢。<br />\n<br />\n分手之後，有一段時間，每逢到外地開會，都會偷偷寄postcard、知道有乜消息都會寫個email，佢都係無覆，所以其實我係咪唔應該再搵佢⋯⋯"},{"pid":"390cf6f1f43e07795780ee52f371cc93b41b1ef9","tid":2395852,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T07:09:43.000Z","msg":"凌晨了，黎睇睇凌晨自貼補補血<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2386762\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2386762</a>"},{"pid":"982a5d1b328184e94124196d9e44ace9a8636fdf","tid":2395852,"uid":30604,"like":106,"dislike":1,"score":105,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T07:10:07.000Z","msg":"搞乜撚 咪撚咁多事啦你"},{"pid":"c4fda9d6ae0f4d7e9b3cc2f4e31b0a91473eda78","tid":2395852,"uid":39710,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T07:10:11.000Z","msg":"咪撚癲啦仲搵人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a4970de83599a867e8609ba7babdcf4068dcdf1","tid":2395852,"uid":70439,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"982a5d1b328184e94124196d9e44ace9a8636fdf","tid":2395852,"uid":30604,"like":106,"dislike":1,"score":105,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T07:10:07.000Z","msg":"搞乜撚 咪撚咁多事啦你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T07:10:40.000Z","msg":"米臭系 呢啲臭雞咪撚理佢啦"},{"pid":"4444cc39682ebc31ca79d76ea5a1858efd012248","tid":2395852,"uid":254852,"like":0,"dislike":40,"score":-40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T07:11:50.000Z","msg":"當時嘅第三者，其實係我嘅朋友，宜家都係無fd做，不過唔知點解，有時諗會唔會自己太小氣，都過左十幾年"},{"pid":"c3f299d1b81a9668e99bd86545c9641398c2b99d